sequenceDiagram
  participant B as Navigateur
  participant V as Vercel Next.js
  participant K as Ktor API
  participant MW as PolicyEnforcerMiddleware
  participant PE as PolicyEvaluator
  participant P as PostgreSQL RLS
  participant AL as AccessAuditLog

  Note over B,P: Authentification
  B->>V: GET /login
  V-->>B: Page login SSR
  B->>K: POST /auth/login email + password
  K->>P: SELECT account WHERE email = ?
  P-->>K: Account row
  K->>K: BCrypt.verify password hash
  K->>K: JWT.generate userId + profileType
  K-->>B: accessToken + refreshToken + expiresIn

  Note over B,AL: Requête authentifiée avec vérification ABAC
  B->>K: GET /dashboard/childId - Authorization Bearer JWT
  K->>MW: Intercepte la requête
  MW->>MW: Extrait UserId + ProfileType du JWT
  MW->>PE: evaluate AccessScope

  PE->>P: SELECT care_relation WHERE observer=userId AND observee=childId AND status=ACTIVE
  
  alt CareRelation ACTIVE
    P-->>PE: CareRelation PARENTAL ACTIVE
    PE->>PE: PermissionMatrix.isAllowed PARENTAL READ DASHBOARD
    PE->>AL: log GRANTED
    PE-->>MW: GRANTED
    MW->>K: Continue vers handler
    K->>P: SELECT alerts + messages + stats WHERE child_id = childId
    Note over P: RLS vérifie aussi la relation : 2e barrière
    P-->>K: Data rows
    K-->>B: DashboardDTO JSON
  end

  alt Pas de relation active
    P-->>PE: null
    PE->>AL: log DENIED No active CareRelation
    PE-->>MW: DENIED
    MW-->>B: HTTP 403 Forbidden
  end

  Note over B,AL: Notifications temps réel
  B->>P: WebSocket connect via Supabase Realtime JWT
  P-->>B: Subscription confirmée
  Note right of P: Un badge est débloqué...
  P-->>B: Event BadgeUnlocked childId badge
